Goldfinger is a Webfinger client for Ruby.  It supports application/xrd+xml and
application/jrd+json responses. It raises Goldfinger::NotFoundError on failure
to fetch the Webfinger or XRD data, or Goldfinger::SSLError if something is
wrong with the HTTPS connection.

WWW: https://github.com/Gargron/goldfinger/
